fields.example: He awoke early in the morning.
He spent a lot of money.
He stuck the poster on the wall.
The child clung to his mother.
She put the book on the table.
The child slid on the ice.
She stuck a note on the wall.
He swore to tell the truth.
The cat sprang onto the table.
The paper stuck to the wall.
She swore to tell the truth.
His ankle swelled after the fall.
The child swung on the swing.
He withdrew money from the bank.
A problem arose during the meeting.
The village was beset by problems.
He bet on the horse race.
He bound the book with string.
They bred horses on the farm.
He cast the net into the sea.
The child clung to his mother.
The spider crept across the floor.
She forgave him for the mistake.
Woe betide anyone who breaks the rules.
The axe cleft the wood in two.
They hewed logs for the fire.
The dragon was slain by the knight.
Clothes were strewn across the room.
She wrung out the wet cloth.

fields.descriptions:
"Can" — ingliz tilidagi modal fe’l bo‘lib, qobiliyat, ehtimollik, ruxsat, so‘rov va taklif ma’nolarini bildiradi.
Kimdir nima qila olishini yoki nima sodir bo‘lishi mumkinligini ko‘rsatadi.
Savol gaplarda ruxsat so‘rash yoki muloyim so‘rov qilish uchun ishlatiladi.
Inkori (cannot / can't) qila olmaslik yoki taqiqni bildiradi.
Har doim asosiy fe’lning infinitive (to-siz) shakli bilan keladi

**"To be" fe'li ingliz tilidagi eng muhim fe'llardan biridir. U shaxs, narsalar yoki holatning holatini ifodalash uchun ishlatiladi.

Hozirgi zamonda u quyidagi shakllarga ega: am, is, are. O‘tgan zamonda esa: was, were.
bu verblar o'tkan zamon shaklida verblarga ed olmaydi va verblarni o'tkan zamondagi shakli hisoblanadai

fields.exemple: Can you help me, please? – Iltimos, menga yordam bera olasizmi?
I can speak English. – Men ingliz tilida gaplasha olaman.
Men talabayman. — I am a student.
